d99dfef6-974e-49ba-95b7-2a2262e02fa6.title: Romeo
d99dfef6-974e-49ba-95b7-2a2262e02fa6.text:
What is to become of me and my darling Juliet, I
cannot find her anywhere, have you seen her?

options.text: Yes, I have seen her actually!
遰 No sorry, I haven't seen her.
Perhaps I could help to find her for you?

dbfd841c-1e77-476d-8470-5684d0354141.title: <player>
dbfd841c-1e77-476d-8470-5684d0354141.text: Yes, I have seen her actually!

f73829db-36b8-4c02-8671-2cd953eb7512.title: <player>
f73829db-36b8-4c02-8671-2cd953eb7512.text: At least, I think it was her... Blonde? A bit stressed?

89ac16a2-e77a-4545-9ecf-06f0834347f2.title: Romeo
89ac16a2-e77a-4545-9ecf-06f0834347f2.text: Golly...yes, yes...you make her sound very interesting!

8ca6a279-9528-4835-a8e0-46a3b9a265aa.title: Romeo
8ca6a279-9528-4835-a8e0-46a3b9a265aa.text: And I'll bet she's a bit of a fox!

f8cebb42-7ac3-4f18-8350-a89cc93bd910.title: <player>
f8cebb42-7ac3-4f18-8350-a89cc93bd910.text: Well, I guess she could be considered attractive...

fe2db918-8438-4023-92b6-1f995cab7f1e.title: Romeo
fe2db918-8438-4023-92b6-1f995cab7f1e.text:
Sorry, all that jubilation has made me forget what we
were talking about.

f517dde1-7700-4668-8b4e-62f8c7a31c9a.title: <player>
f517dde1-7700-4668-8b4e-62f8c7a31c9a.text:
You were asking me about Juliet? You seemed to know
her?

d74ac0ba-f592-4eda-bbd6-b42c71c44d50.title: Romeo
d74ac0ba-f592-4eda-bbd6-b42c71c44d50.text:
The fox...could you tell her that she is the love of my
long and that I life to be with her?

b171d6b2-35a8-49b2-bed9-86a7ae232865.title: <player>
b171d6b2-35a8-49b2-bed9-86a7ae232865.text:
What? 
Surely you mean that she is the love of your life and
that you long to be with her?

b4ea8ac7-19e8-43bf-87f1-ef037de1e032.title: Romeo
b4ea8ac7-19e8-43bf-87f1-ef037de1e032.text:
Oh yeah...what you said...tell her that, it sounds much
better! 
Oh you're so good at this!

options.text: 遰 Yes, ok, I'll let her know.
Sorry Romeo, I've got better things to do right now but maybe later?

4d2895f5-121f-459d-805b-16f2adf7de09.title: <player>
4d2895f5-121f-459d-805b-16f2adf7de09.text: No sorry, I haven't seen her.

8e007afc-0ca9-45c4-894c-b12860dde162.title: Romeo
8e007afc-0ca9-45c4-894c-b12860dde162.text: Oh...well, that's a shame...I was rather hoping you had.

c41b32f9-1d21-4292-bb5f-19707ee013ab.title: <player>
c41b32f9-1d21-4292-bb5f-19707ee013ab.text:
Why? 
Is she a fugitive? 
Does she owe you some money or something?

5248b0f2-58dd-4b26-a4db-5a3c3d8b4f21.title: Romeo
5248b0f2-58dd-4b26-a4db-5a3c3d8b4f21.text:
Hmmm, she might do? 
Perhaps she does? 
How do you know?

28d618f1-3444-4641-9f77-fdd199b234c0.title: <player>
28d618f1-3444-4641-9f77-fdd199b234c0.text:
I don't know? I was asking 'YOU' how 'YOU' know
Juliet!

bc65d2de-e84b-4725-a8be-70e8ed5944c2.title: Romeo
bc65d2de-e84b-4725-a8be-70e8ed5944c2.text:
Ahh, yes Juliet, she's my one true love. 
Well, one of my one true loves! If you see her, could
you tell her that she is the love of my long and that I
life to be with her?

69000f80-a4b9-4bc2-b03c-800ecdbf1e84.title: <player>
69000f80-a4b9-4bc2-b03c-800ecdbf1e84.text:
Perhaps I can help find her for you? What does she
look like?

43e19818-49f3-4ad1-9ae2-1f4ac90b264e.title: Romeo
43e19818-49f3-4ad1-9ae2-1f4ac90b264e.text:
Oh would you? That would be great! She has this sort
of hair...

70f530f1-5938-4a7d-a670-3463a05e1690.title: <player>
70f530f1-5938-4a7d-a670-3463a05e1690.text: Oh and she has these lovely shoulders as well..

f7622ba4-8d36-4560-aa32-a5b32f581837.title: Romeo
f7622ba4-8d36-4560-aa32-a5b32f581837.text:
Shoulders...right, so she has hair, lips and shoulders...that
should cut it down a bit.

c2eda177-6e67-43d5-8401-8ccf5fb2315a.title: Romeo
c2eda177-6e67-43d5-8401-8ccf5fb2315a.text:
Oh yes, Juliet is very different...please tell her that she
is the love of my long and that I life to be with her?

2266551a-a8eb-4002-a7f3-3cc0139cd76f.title: <player>
2266551a-a8eb-4002-a7f3-3cc0139cd76f.text:
Sorry Romeo, I've got better things to do right now
but maybe later?

d3c73922-0a13-431d-8f0f-d0d5b76e4823.title: Romeo
d3c73922-0a13-431d-8f0f-d0d5b76e4823.text:
Oh, ok, well, I guess my Juliet and I can spend some
time apart. 
And as the old saying goes, 'Absinthe makes the heart
glow longer'.

8f7d5f25-39bc-4b49-abab-f33d8084efb3.title: <player>
8f7d5f25-39bc-4b49-abab-f33d8084efb3.text: Don't you mean that, 'Absence makes the...

f1f7786f-be12-4cca-b802-479c48b68fbf.title: Romeo
f1f7786f-be12-4cca-b802-479c48b68fbf.text:
Sadness surrounds me now that Juliet's father forbids
us to meet. Have you seen my Juliet?

b8daba8c-9fc6-4e4f-8c01-c09de2976bbd.title: Romeo
b8daba8c-9fc6-4e4f-8c01-c09de2976bbd.text: Blub! Blub...where is my Juliet? Have you seen her?

46b4b3a3-5e6d-45a4-8914-351fb22324a7.title: Romeo
46b4b3a3-5e6d-45a4-8914-351fb22324a7.text:
Oh woe is me that I cannot find my Juliet! You haven't
seen Juliet have you?

491ce2b4-55a3-46c4-8a15-4a35f1fa6a47.title: Romeo
491ce2b4-55a3-46c4-8a15-4a35f1fa6a47.text:
Juliet, Juliet, wherefore art thou Juliet? Have you
seen my Juliet?

6533743a-5f30-4998-8e51-7a626b106934.title: Romeo
6533743a-5f30-4998-8e51-7a626b106934.text:
Looking for a blonde girl, goes by the name of
Juliet..quite pretty...haven't seen her have you?

a7deacff-e55c-4c5a-a391-53c297d51c34.title: <player>
a7deacff-e55c-4c5a-a391-53c297d51c34.text: Yes, ok, I'll let her know.

8c2ee0db-1377-44e9-8534-37b2303fa06b.title: Romeo
8c2ee0db-1377-44e9-8534-37b2303fa06b.text: Oh great! And tell her that I want to kiss her a give.

3ac66d40-de02-46f3-894a-905a86905ab9.title: <player>
3ac66d40-de02-46f3-894a-905a86905ab9.text: You mean you want to give her a kiss!

45f6cc5a-7071-4bb3-ad0a-e6c01d4e10a9.title: Romeo
45f6cc5a-7071-4bb3-ad0a-e6c01d4e10a9.text: I see I've picked a true professional...!

b3ca6262-0e03-49b3-ac55-3b39b8bf4bb7.title: <player>
b3ca6262-0e03-49b3-ac55-3b39b8bf4bb7.text: You haven't got a clue who I am do you?

f9861391-0d5c-44c8-a175-c55fe2617401.title: Romeo
f9861391-0d5c-44c8-a175-c55fe2617401.text:
Not a clue my friend, but you seem to have a friendly
face...a little blood stained, and perhaps in need of a
wash, but friendly none the less.

0539cab3-9b08-4702-8fcc-25f9a400bc0c.title: <player>
0539cab3-9b08-4702-8fcc-25f9a400bc0c.text: You asked me to look for Juliet for you!

2231aaaf-5fed-42a8-b0ed-768066849415.title: Romeo
2231aaaf-5fed-42a8-b0ed-768066849415.text: Ah yes, Juliet...my sweet darling...what news?

ffb1b485-1395-41a4-a5d9-50b25a2f238c.title: <player>
ffb1b485-1395-41a4-a5d9-50b25a2f238c.text: Nothing so far, but I need to ask a few questions?

options.text: Is there anything else you can tell me about Juliet?

d7bda6d2-6656-4918-bc2f-090c2ffae711.title: <player>
d7bda6d2-6656-4918-bc2f-090c2ffae711.text: So that I can try and find her for you!

f976cfb7-dc9d-4ddf-b01f-b4b4cf46a0bc.title: Romeo
f976cfb7-dc9d-4ddf-b01f-b4b4cf46a0bc.text: Ah yes....quite right. Hmmm, let me think now.

3b1fd5d1-25fd-4dda-9dda-a0d6f8be97f5.title: Romeo
3b1fd5d1-25fd-4dda-9dda-a0d6f8be97f5.text:
She may still be locked away at her Father's house on
the sest vide of Warrock.

0f0c84c6-6ffc-4b86-9a12-1470a557c08e.title: Romeo
0f0c84c6-6ffc-4b86-9a12-1470a557c08e.text:
Oh, I remember how she loved it when I would sing up
to her balcony! She would reward me with her own
personal items...

6d36c3f7-e046-4340-8972-92347f69a10d.title: <player>
6d36c3f7-e046-4340-8972-92347f69a10d.text: What, she just gave you her stuff?

72b56dc6-4186-4553-ba45-752bea384e91.title: Romeo
72b56dc6-4186-4553-ba45-752bea384e91.text:
Well, not exactly give...more like 'throw with considerable
force'...she's always a kidder that Juliet!

c3a58061-33ef-461f-b91a-5aeedef59d26.title: <player>
c3a58061-33ef-461f-b91a-5aeedef59d26.text: Is there anything else you can tell me about Juliet?

caa94fee-0c3d-44eb-be1c-67ea0e103c4b.title: Romeo
caa94fee-0c3d-44eb-be1c-67ea0e103c4b.text:
Oh, there is so much to tell...she is my true love, we
intend to spend together forever...I can tell you so
much about her..

c3f66aa5-17bc-42e4-ae86-7eb9ad91b5b8.title: <player>
c3f66aa5-17bc-42e4-ae86-7eb9ad91b5b8.text:
Romeo...great news...I've been in touch with Juliet!
She's written a message for you...

5a66717f-d072-4fe2-861e-810797663f1f.text: You hand over Juliet's message to Romeo.

30c634a2-72ad-4cdc-83f8-014fa3cbe41a.title: Romeo
30c634a2-72ad-4cdc-83f8-014fa3cbe41a.text:
Oh, a message! A message! I've never had a message
before...

443366ee-e8c1-428c-b0dc-327619db53a1.title: Romeo
443366ee-e8c1-428c-b0dc-327619db53a1.text: Oh, well, except for the occasional court summons.

15469d78-1da0-4572-82e9-a2c2381f585c.title: Romeo
15469d78-1da0-4572-82e9-a2c2381f585c.text:
But they're not really 'nice' messages. Not like this one!
I'm sure that this message will be lovely.

f5660e6f-64d1-4a8e-a9e7-1d0190e0c97f.title: <player>
f5660e6f-64d1-4a8e-a9e7-1d0190e0c97f.text: Well are you going to open it or not?

c33db9eb-7175-4850-b5a8-0b255c437f64.title: Romeo
c33db9eb-7175-4850-b5a8-0b255c437f64.text:
Oh yes, yes, of course! 
'Dearest Romeo, I am very pleased that you sent
<player> to look for me and to tell me that you still
hold affliction...', Affliction! She thinks I'm diseased?

55464c3b-6331-4d75-aebe-0a86f2c0f5dc.title: Romeo
55464c3b-6331-4d75-aebe-0a86f2c0f5dc.text:
Ahh yes...'still hold affection for me. I still feel great
affection for you, but unfortunately my Father opposes
our marriage.'

85700942-3699-4503-94ea-ca5d12cd3ea1.title: <player>
85700942-3699-4503-94ea-ca5d12cd3ea1.text: Oh dear...that doesn't sound too good.

d1e64163-e2e9-4ca3-85ab-ddd3e0a6d5df.title: Romeo
d1e64163-e2e9-4ca3-85ab-ddd3e0a6d5df.text: What? '...great affection for you. Father opposes our..

4a14a879-b59b-4e2a-a7df-5abe1c93d93d.title: Romeo
4a14a879-b59b-4e2a-a7df-5abe1c93d93d.text: ...will kill you if he sees you again!'

682b64eb-a141-4c4d-839f-c7347a18c5d3.title: <player>
682b64eb-a141-4c4d-839f-c7347a18c5d3.text: I have to be honest, it's not getting any better..

eec42cbd-a6dd-43c7-8bbc-d949aa254f38.title: Romeo
eec42cbd-a6dd-43c7-8bbc-d949aa254f38.text:
'Our only hope is that Father Lawrence, our long time
confidant, can help us in some way.'

1a506d5d-e010-4f2c-a852-82375730e880.title: Romeo
1a506d5d-e010-4f2c-a852-82375730e880.text: Well, that's it then...we haven't got a chance...

75fb40d8-e24a-4ee2-aa4b-49647b14ec1b.title: Romeo
75fb40d8-e24a-4ee2-aa4b-49647b14ec1b.text:
...our love is over...the great romance, the life of my
love...

0fac9f8e-8489-48fe-83c8-acba6cb03043.title: <player>
0fac9f8e-8489-48fe-83c8-acba6cb03043.text: ...or you could speak to Father Lawrence!

307a26e5-c693-4592-9e98-209aabfefa4e.title: Romeo
307a26e5-c693-4592-9e98-209aabfefa4e.text:
Oh, my aching, breaking, heart...how useless the situation
is now...we have no one to turn to...

80da31e8-fc76-4501-a383-4c9cfb4e4f2c.title: Romeo
80da31e8-fc76-4501-a383-4c9cfb4e4f2c.text:
Oh yes, Father Lawrence...he's our long time confidant,
he might have a solution! Yes, yes, you have to go and
talk to Lather Fawrence for us and ask him if he's got
any suggestions for our predicament?

ace5d923-9de2-4bc3-9d07-611ebb24bc74.title: <player>
ace5d923-9de2-4bc3-9d07-611ebb24bc74.text: Where can I find Father Lawrence?

ce898a5f-b6ed-4916-9cfc-4d7fd358a9c2.title: Romeo
ce898a5f-b6ed-4916-9cfc-4d7fd358a9c2.text: You know he's not my 'real' Father don't you?

465ad12d-0d4f-4e2c-8256-9436c0b40e78.title: <player>
465ad12d-0d4f-4e2c-8256-9436c0b40e78.text: I think I suspected that he wasn't.

b81f6d01-1832-45c2-8406-d5db666ef7a5.title: Romeo
b81f6d01-1832-45c2-8406-d5db666ef7a5.text:
Well anyway...he tells these song, loring bermons...and
keeps these here Carrockian vitizens snoring in his
church to the East North.

bb5888c0-b395-45e6-a256-81499544f41b.title: <player>
bb5888c0-b395-45e6-a256-81499544f41b.text: Romeo...great news...I've been in touch with Juliet!

408f144e-d5e8-44d7-9baf-8d1991677ef0.title: Romeo
408f144e-d5e8-44d7-9baf-8d1991677ef0.text:
Oh great! That is great news! Well done...well done...
what a total success!

14258d12-ed80-4940-b4a1-c2724967adcb.title: <player>
14258d12-ed80-4940-b4a1-c2724967adcb.text: Yes, and she gave me a message to give you...

3ec0c369-47ae-44e5-9fcb-7f0fdc1b7b48.title: Romeo
3ec0c369-47ae-44e5-9fcb-7f0fdc1b7b48.text:
A message...oh, I can't wait to read what my dear Juliet
has to say....

906c2a88-676e-4396-8780-f4436d6b1cde.title: Romeo
906c2a88-676e-4396-8780-f4436d6b1cde.text: You've lost the message haven't you?

32a1db05-144d-44f8-b853-42c12131508c.title: <player>
32a1db05-144d-44f8-b853-42c12131508c.text: Yep, haven't got a clue where it is.

options.text: Where can I find Father Lawrence?
Have you heard anything from Juliet?

523d97a0-462d-4f98-a27b-41fb8737cbd7.title: Romeo
523d97a0-462d-4f98-a27b-41fb8737cbd7.text: Not so good my friend...I miss Judi..., Junie..., Joopie...

7262f518-0203-4846-b559-e7f327b4cb68.title: Romeo
7262f518-0203-4846-b559-e7f327b4cb68.text: You know he's not my 'real' Father don't you?

7df97330-6e27-4289-95e9-cc7bb6a9790d.title: <player>
7df97330-6e27-4289-95e9-cc7bb6a9790d.text: I think I suspected that he wasn't.

7a88fa45-2827-4fca-9b4e-d34d637e7a94.title: Romeo
7a88fa45-2827-4fca-9b4e-d34d637e7a94.text:
Well anyway...he tells these song, loring bermons...and
keeps these here Carrockian vitizens snoring in his
church to the East North.

1a2c918c-baec-422a-bbf8-816a28cce023.title: <player>
1a2c918c-baec-422a-bbf8-816a28cce023.text: Have you heard anything from Juliet?

4f9b0c97-381a-4dbc-a2be-02a84d738783.title: Romeo
4f9b0c97-381a-4dbc-a2be-02a84d738783.text:
Sadly not my friend! And what's worse, her Father has
threatened to kill me if he sees me. I mean, that seems
a bit harsh!

a3a6d343-7923-4ff5-8afb-91fdb1298cbd.title: <player>
a3a6d343-7923-4ff5-8afb-91fdb1298cbd.text:
Well, I shouldn't worry too much...you can always run
away if you see him...

c4c39e75-7743-4a37-8211-54259005cf06.title: Romeo
c4c39e75-7743-4a37-8211-54259005cf06.text:
I just wish I could remember what he looks like! I live
in fear of every man I see!

78a676e2-7879-4251-a15c-a33005f38618.title: Romeo
78a676e2-7879-4251-a15c-a33005f38618.text:
Ooh did you manage to survive one of Lather
Fawrences sermons? I bet not, you were ages! I bet
you snoozed on the welcome mat just as soon as you
heard his voice!

8caf662a-ff85-4b8b-a825-60a20a02dc80.title: Romeo
8caf662a-ff85-4b8b-a825-60a20a02dc80.text: Oh, come on, come on, what did he say?

options.text: He wants me to go to the Apothecary!
He seems keen for you to marry Juliet.

0f679aa0-4b94-4b93-86d9-bd7814d82cd2.title: <player>
0f679aa0-4b94-4b93-86d9-bd7814d82cd2.text: He seems very keen for you to marry Juliet.

6d1219c4-70b4-474c-8ce8-9e2768b65ffd.title: Romeo
6d1219c4-70b4-474c-8ce8-9e2768b65ffd.text: Me too! I can't wait! Do you think it will be soon?

26dde4b8-9c12-44cf-bea9-1c63302a8671.title: <player>
26dde4b8-9c12-44cf-bea9-1c63302a8671.text:
I don't know, but I'll do what I can. It just seems a bit
odd that Father Lawrence is so keen for you to marry?

b4318350-b4b6-4d84-bf8a-5b9484970efa.title: Romeo
b4318350-b4b6-4d84-bf8a-5b9484970efa.text:
I can't imagine why he's so keen? Though, he was our
messenger before you. Of course, he had a lot more
hair back then...and I think we may have gone to school
together...

f3cc7d8f-0711-40ba-812e-c1529663c87a.title: Romeo
f3cc7d8f-0711-40ba-812e-c1529663c87a.text:
Yeah! Thinking about it now, we called him 'Diddy
Dorrence' back then!

055ba18e-5bb7-4da6-894d-668e5a5ae95d.title: <player>
055ba18e-5bb7-4da6-894d-668e5a5ae95d.text:
So, maybe, he just wants a bit of peace? And when you
two are married, he won't have to traipse around
delivering your messages anymore?

250b3236-6c46-4391-be39-b2bfb6f2d6d5.title: Romeo
250b3236-6c46-4391-be39-b2bfb6f2d6d5.text: Yes, the years haven't been good to him.

5cac6e8a-ede5-4202-9d0d-5eb7db4f6367.title: <player>
5cac6e8a-ede5-4202-9d0d-5eb7db4f6367.text: He wants me to go to the Apothecary!

4ad49d8f-b626-4a01-8a63-ce72eb96691d.title: Romeo
4ad49d8f-b626-4a01-8a63-ce72eb96691d.text:
Oh...is he the one who mixes up all them magical potion-
ey things?

6553275d-419f-4943-b513-6bcd32312896.title: <player>
6553275d-419f-4943-b513-6bcd32312896.text: Yeah, I think so...but the word potion-ey doesn't exist.

603a0679-6a3a-416e-9b86-64433830bf78.title: Romeo
603a0679-6a3a-416e-9b86-64433830bf78.text: Well, you just used it...so I guess it does exist!

88948b17-c024-4fa7-881c-bc47375de668.title: <player>
88948b17-c024-4fa7-881c-bc47375de668.text:
It doesn't matter...do you know where the Apothecary
is?

8164fdc8-c926-4f2f-b4e2-05877ac40316.title: <player>
8164fdc8-c926-4f2f-b4e2-05877ac40316.text: Because I'm doing you a favour!

749c6b06-15fe-4259-bedb-048f78386069.title: Romeo
749c6b06-15fe-4259-bedb-048f78386069.text:
Right, yes...of course! Well, I think the potion-ey place
is Wouth Sest of here and near a sword shop.

3d38e708-69d7-4201-b95b-c2e709947619.title: Romeo
3d38e708-69d7-4201-b95b-c2e709947619.text:
Ooohh, that's the potion is it?
Rather you than me!

6f29f639-e0d2-4145-ad3e-a13949c8a083.title: <player>
6f29f639-e0d2-4145-ad3e-a13949c8a083.text: I'm not drinking it! It's for Juliet!

75f16137-278d-4db9-a7cd-5403fe499a0b.title: Romeo
75f16137-278d-4db9-a7cd-5403fe499a0b.text:
Well, I mean...it's probably delicious...and not dangerous
at all. And you quite often see harmless drinks in a
glowing sort of pink colour.

44147edc-90b9-49dc-85fe-3800d37802ed.title: <player>
44147edc-90b9-49dc-85fe-3800d37802ed.text:
Hmm, I'm not convinced...maybe you ought to try
some before I give it to Juliet?

3e33a86a-70d3-4c2f-8f22-0a5ca13e558d.title: Romeo
3e33a86a-70d3-4c2f-8f22-0a5ca13e558d.text:
Urgh! No way! 
Not in a million years!

ceec3c55-7486-4c3d-941e-607c8c2ecc86.title: <player>
ceec3c55-7486-4c3d-941e-607c8c2ecc86.text:
Ok...but you know what to do when I've given this to
Juliet?

e24c483e-cce3-4109-a062-fdc7c68149d1.title: Romeo
e24c483e-cce3-4109-a062-fdc7c68149d1.text:
Oh, yeah...sure Lather Fawrence explained all that to
me..

83e92716-30d8-4d27-84b2-32a12f4238c1.title: Romeo
83e92716-30d8-4d27-84b2-32a12f4238c1.text: Oh hello, have you seen Lather Fawrence?

40c764f1-4d65-4900-b3f4-b18b1cfd469b.title: <player>
40c764f1-4d65-4900-b3f4-b18b1cfd469b.text:
Yes, he's given me details of a potion which should help
resolve this situation. The Apothecary is helping me
prepare it.

e1a3cac1-815a-40d5-b23c-ef469cd01352.title: Romeo
e1a3cac1-815a-40d5-b23c-ef469cd01352.text: Ooooh, it all sounds horribly complicated?

3cadca42-f7e2-432a-821d-bb9c38b16fbd.title: Romeo
3cadca42-f7e2-432a-821d-bb9c38b16fbd.text:
All I can say is I'll be glad when Juliet's finally in that
crypt!

1c7ce411-fe53-4eb0-bbfe-e5541441d782.title: <player>
1c7ce411-fe53-4eb0-bbfe-e5541441d782.text:
Romeo, it's all set. Juliet has drunk the potion and has
been taken down into the Crypt...now you just need to
pop along and collect her.

2cc8ef73-b025-412b-ab39-fceb2fccba0e.title: Romeo
2cc8ef73-b025-412b-ab39-fceb2fccba0e.text: What potion would that be then?

353ac12d-36e3-4ca9-8d06-544c13911fed.title: <player>
353ac12d-36e3-4ca9-8d06-544c13911fed.text:
The Cadava potion...you know, the one which will make
her appear dead! She's in the crypt, pop along and claim
your true love.

572fb1aa-0b98-4973-8e27-7b5170b6162b.title: Romeo
572fb1aa-0b98-4973-8e27-7b5170b6162b.text: But I'm scared...will you come with me?

9475972c-7a99-4949-aa42-302072ac7bc5.title: <player>
9475972c-7a99-4949-aa42-302072ac7bc5.text:
Oh , ok...come on! I think I saw the entrance when I
visited there last...

bd7b2753-e622-4d8e-84e7-141ae0c83c99.title: <player>
bd7b2753-e622-4d8e-84e7-141ae0c83c99.text: We're here. Look, Juliet is over there!

eb02f6d2-19f3-47ca-8647-eea4e7ded3dc.title: <player>
eb02f6d2-19f3-47ca-8647-eea4e7ded3dc.text: You go over to her...and I'll go and wait over here...

15184479-c54e-45d9-ac11-cdc283893723.title: Romeo
15184479-c54e-45d9-ac11-cdc283893723.text: Oh dear...you seem to be dead.

ad82bc85-d708-496a-8c9b-c09832082fae.title: Phillipa
ad82bc85-d708-496a-8c9b-c09832082fae.text:
It's a shame about Juliet...but perhaps we can meet up
later?

1522ad72-4ad4-4169-834c-a30192eab1b7.title: Romeo
1522ad72-4ad4-4169-834c-a30192eab1b7.text: I heard Juliet had died. Terrible business.

77903e6d-dd72-4cf8-b9e3-914825d242e8.title: Romeo
77903e6d-dd72-4cf8-b9e3-914825d242e8.text:
Her cousin and I are getting on well though. Thanks
for your help.
